From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Nickel Browser: Disable Crash Reporter

This patch disables Google's crash reporting infrastructure.

---
 chrome/browser/metrics/metrics_reporting_state.cc | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/chrome/browser/metrics/metrics_reporting_state.cc b/chrome/browser/metrics/metrics_reporting_state.cc
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/chrome/browser/metrics/metrics_reporting_state.cc
+++ b/chrome/browser/metrics/metrics_reporting_state.cc
@@ -25,6 +25,10 @@

 namespace {

+bool IsCrashReporterEnabled() {
+  return false;
+}
+
 void SetMetricsReporting(bool enabled) {
   // Nickel: Forced disabled
   enabled = false;
--
2.40.0
